  issuance schema (schema/usmc-issuance-1.0.xsd).

  The current edition (Effective August 7, 2025, "Military Leave, Liberty, and
  Administrative Absence") reissues and cancels the June 16, 2009 edition
  ("Leave and Liberty Policy and Procedures") that MARADMIN 051/23 and DTM 23-001
  cite by number; DTM 23-001 was to be incorporated into this instruction.

  SCOPE: the Purpose is encoded in full, and the complete Section/paragraph
  structure is encoded from the table of contents (headings are verbatim; status
  VERIFIED as to their existence and titles). Section and paragraph BODIES are
  large and NOT yet encoded. The current parental-leave procedures live at
  3.11.c (ADPL) and 3.11.d (IDPL).
-->
